title: Son killed, father critically injured after Auburn drive-by...
text:
A 17-year-old boy died and his father was critically injured -- during an Auburn drive-by shooting.
A second son was present as well, but was not injured in the shooting.
Initially, police reported two people had been killed.
Only one dead in Auburn 17 yo... Father is in bad shape pic.twitter.com/BBJh6g47Gk
— Henry Rosoff (@HenryKIRO7) October 21, 2015 Auburn police were investigating—as of 5:30 p.m.
>> This story is developing.
